My father was A1C Jerry Dean Olds. Killed 5 June 1966 <br>
25 miles south of DaNang.  He and six other men were en<br>
route to survey for a radar site when they were ambushed.<br>
I would like to communicate with anyone that knew him. <br>
He played guitar in Nam for a band called &quot;The Sky Raiders.&quot;<br>
He was from Lauderdale County, Tennessee, but enlisted from<br>
Elizabethtown, Kentucky.  Sent to Vietnam out of Hastings,<br>
Nebraska Air Force Base.  
